314
00:12:14,916 --> 00:12:17,166
I have noticed

315
00:12:17,625 --> 00:12:18,833
your achievements in talent cultivation.

316
00:12:19,083 --> 00:12:19,875
So I intend to

317
00:12:19,875 --> 00:12:21,875
