334
00:13:07,791 --> 00:13:08,708
It’s a good idea.

335
00:13:09,125 --> 00:13:10,125
Then I accept your invitation.

336
00:13:10,875 --> 00:13:11,833
But I have a condition.

337
00:13:12,416 --> 00:13:14,416
