371
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:27,083
Hello?

372
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:28,000
Sichen.

373
00:14:29,416 --> 00:14:30,333
What’re you doing?

374
00:14:32,333 --> 00:14:33,625
Reading files.

375
00:14:34,375 --> 00:14:35,708
But it’s so late.

376
00:14:36,333 --> 00:14:37,050
I’m busy today.

377
00:14:39,416 --> 00:14:42,750
