382
00:14:48,125 --> 00:14:48,650
I’m not angry.

383
00:14:48,958 --> 00:14:49,833
So nice of you.

384
00:14:50,791 --> 00:14:52,375
Do you feel depressed?

385
00:14:52,708 --> 00:14:53,291
No.

386
00:14:54,250 --> 00:14:55,666
Do you miss me?

387
00:14:55,833 --> 00:14:56,425
No.

388
