476
00:18:52,375 --> 00:18:53,750
I would have brought Fei’ang with me.

477
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:57,000
Gu Xixi, you’re killing me.

478
00:19:00,850 --> 00:19:01,775
(Mr. Zorro:)

479
00:19:01,775 --> 00:19:03,500
(Hello, Gu Xixi took a sick leave.
