fried dough sticks and soybean milk?

512
00:21:58,291 --> 00:21:58,833
Mr. Mo.

513
00:21:59,041 --> 00:22:00,375
Won’t you invite Miss Gu

514
00:22:00,416 --> 00:22:01,541
