553
00:23:59,150 --> 00:24:00,475
(Mr. Zorro)
How about an extra dish?

554
00:24:00,475 --> 00:24:01,025
(Mr. Zorro)
OK.

555
00:24:01,025 --> 00:24:01,650
(Mr. Zorro)
OK.

556
00:24:01,650 --> 00:24:02,550
(Gu Xixi, I have to see you now!)
Waitress!

